&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for an enthusiastic and motivated Nurse, with previous experience in a senior role in radiology, to join the department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be expected to be a state registered nurse who oversees the fundamentals of care for all patients and take a lead in the implementation of practice protocols within Imaging across four departments and two sites within the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The candidate should display excellent organisational and communication skills and a high level of clinical and professional leadership within the clinical area. A commitment to professional development will also be expected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please note that this post is subject to a 6 month probationary period.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rachel Mason, Imaging Manager on 020 39470185 or email rachel.mason12@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
